Name: Fishy Business
About the game: Fishy Business - You are a cool mafia fish who goes on another ordinary fish business. Take your gun and shoot all opponents while collecting their skulls in this crazy platformer! You will need not only accurate shooting at enemies, but also the ability to accurately jump on the platforms, avoiding the traps of the underwater world. Peculiarities: - Nice graphics by Feryu - Nice soundtrack
